---
layout: layouts/page.njk
title: "Quote calculator"
description: "Get an online price estimate for fire sealing — choose opening type, wall type, fire rating and dimensions."
eleventyNavigation:
  key: quote-en
  order: 4
---
<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="bg" style="background-image: url('/img/documentation.jpg');"></div>
  <div class="scrim"></div>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="crumbs"><a href="/en/">Home</a> &nbsp;/&nbsp; <span>Quote calculator</span></div>
    <h1>Quote calculator.</h1>
    <p class="kicker">Get an online price estimate — choose the opening type, wall type, fire rating and dimensions. We'll send the quote to your email instantly.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="quoter-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="quoter-intro">
      <div>
        <div class="label">How it works</div>
        <h2>An estimated price in three minutes.</h2>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p>Add one row for each type of opening in your project. Choose the opening type, wall, fire rating and dimensions — the calculator computes an estimated price automatically.</p>
        <div class="notice">
          <strong>Note:</strong> This is an estimated price. The final price is confirmed with an on-site inspection. Prices exclude VAT.
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <form class="quoter" id="quoter" data-lang="{{ lang }}">
      <div class="quoter-header">
        <span>Opening type</span>
        <span>Wall type</span>
        <span>Fire rating</span>
        <span class="r">Width&nbsp;(cm)</span>
        <span class="r">Height&nbsp;(cm)</span>
        <span>From floor</span>
        <span class="r">Qty</span>
        <span class="r">Price</span>
        <span></span>
      </div>

      <div class="quoter-rows" id="quoter-rows"></div>

      <div class="quoter-actions">
        <button type="button" class="add-row" data-quoter-add>+ Add a row</button>
      </div>

      <div class="quoter-total">
        <div>
          <div class="label-block">Estimated total</div>
          <div class="small">Excl. VAT · estimated from your selections</div>
        </div>
        <div class="total-amount" id="total-amount">0 ISK</div>
      </div>

      <div class="quoter-customer">
        <h3>Send the estimated quote</h3>
        <div class="grid">
          <input type="text" name="cust-name" placeholder="Name" required>
          <input type="text" name="cust-company" placeholder="Company / Project name">
          <input type="email" name="cust-email" placeholder="Email" required>
          <input type="tel" name="cust-phone" placeholder="Phone">
        </div>
        <textarea name="cust-notes" placeholder="Notes, project location, timeline…"></textarea>

        <div class="submit-row">
          <span class="note">You'll receive a confirmation by email and a project manager will call within 24 hours.</span>
          <button type="submit" class="submit-btn">
            <span>Send quote</span>
            <span class="arrow">→</span>
          </button>
        </div>

        <div class="quoter-confirm" id="quoter-confirm">
          ✓ Thanks! Your estimated quote has been sent to your email. A project manager will call within 24 hours.
        </div>
      </div>
    </form>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="cta-band">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <h2>Need an on-site inspection? <span class="ul">Let's talk.</span></h2>
      <div class="actions">
        <a class="btn primary" href="#contact"><span>Request an inspection</span> <span class="arrow">→</span></a>
        <a class="btn ghost" href="tel:+3548504405"><span>(+354) 850-4405</span> <span class="arrow">→</span></a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
